name: Jaden Self-Titled EP
description:
Jaden Track Listing:
1. Battle
2. Rescue Me
3. A Sudden Change of Heart
4. What Remains
5. Take It In
6. of Art and Self

Jaden's first full debut Self-Titled EP release features 6 original songs including a remastered version of "Battle" and "A Sudden Change of Heart" in a full color, 4 panel digipak housing. Join Jaden as they follow through with their melodic yet heavy tone.
